Irish MMA fighter Conor McGregor threw out a disastrous first pitch at Wrigley Field on Tuesday. McGregor, dressed in a suit, sent the baseball hurtling high into the air – and sideways – before the Chicago Cubs’ 9-5 loss to the Minnesota Twins. Watch the pitch here: Twitter users jabbed the UFC star, with some even joking it was worse than that time he tried to throw a football: Check out some of the reactions here: